author: The Associated Press
title: Soccer team from Wuhan returns home nearly 4 months later
description: The Wuhan Zall soccer returned home this weekend after the Chinese government lifted the last restrictions on movement in the city where the COVID-19 outbreak emerged late last year.
content:
The soccer team based in the epicentre of the coronavirus pandemic in China is back home, nearly four months after it left for a preseason tour and got stuck abroad.
